    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development, by reason of its close proximity to dwellings in Stockton House, its excessive height, bulk and scale with a two-storey blank wall, would have an adverse impact on the outlook, sense of enclosure and visual amenity of those neighboring dwellings contrary to National Planning Policy Framework (2021), Policy D3 of the London Plan (2021), Core Policy CS1 (B) of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), policy DM1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013) and the adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010).",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed additional storey, reason of its bulk, massing and unsatisfactory design would result in unsympathetic, incongruous and bulky form of development that fails to respect the character, composition and design of the host building and the surrounding area, contrary to the high quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2021), Policy D3 of the London Plan (2021), Core Policy CS1 (B) of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), policy DM 1 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013) and the adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010)."
